---
import DefaultLayout from '@layouts/DefaultLayout.astro'
---

<DefaultLayout
	title="Objetos II - UNAHUR"
	description="Universidad Nacional de Hurlingham, materia Programación con Objetos II"
	author="Objetos II">
	<section
		class="hero-section relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-unahur-primary to-unahur-secondary py-20 text-white">
		<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
			<div
				class="absolute left-10 top-20 h-32 w-32 animate-pulse rounded-full bg-white">
			</div>
			<div
				class="absolute bottom-20 right-10 h-24 w-24 animate-bounce rounded-full bg-unahur-accent">
			</div>
			<div class="absolute left-1/4 top-1/2 h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-white">
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="container relative z-10 mx-auto px-4">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl text-center">
				<div class="mb-8 flex justify-center">
					<div
						class="animate-on-load rounded-2xl bg-white/20 p-6 backdrop-blur-sm">
						<svg
							class="h-16 w-16 text-white"
							fill="none"
							stroke="currentColor"
							viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path
								stroke-linecap="round"
								stroke-linejoin="round"
								stroke-width="2"
								d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.746 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"
							></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
				</div>

				<h1
					class="animate-on-load mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-blue-100 bg-clip-text text-5xl font-bold text-transparent md:text-7xl">
					Programación con Objetos II
				</h1>

				<p
					class="animate-on-load mb-8 text-xl leading-relaxed text-blue-100 md:text-2xl">
					Universidad Nacional de Hurlingham
				</p>

				<div
					class="animate-on-load flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
					<a
						href="/material"
						class="transform rounded-lg bg-white px-8 py-3 font-semibold text-unahur-primary shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:bg-blue-50">
						📚 Material de Estudio
					</a>
					<a
						href="/videos"
						class="transform rounded-lg border-2 border-white/30 bg-white/10 px-8 py-3 font-semibold text-white shadow-lg backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:border-white/50 hover:bg-white/20">
						🎥 Videos Tutoriales
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section
		class="animate-on-load bg-gray-50 py-16 dark:bg-gray-900"
		data-animate="fade-in-up">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
				<div
					class="animate-on-load mb-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-xl dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800">
					<div class="mb-8 text-center">
						<h2
							class="animate-on-load mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-unahur-primary to-unahur-secondary bg-clip-text text-4xl font-bold text-transparent">
							¡Bienvenido/a!
						</h2>
						<div
							class="animate-on-load mx-auto h-1 w-24 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-unahur-primary to-unahur-secondary">
						</div>
					</div>

					<div
						class="animate-on-load space-y-6 leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
						<p class="text-lg">
							Si llegaste hasta este sitio es muy probable que estés inscripto
							en
							<strong class="text-unahur-primary dark:text-unahur-accent"
								>Programación con Objetos II</strong
							>, de la Licenciatura en Informática de la Universidad Nacional de
							Hurlingham. Aquí encontrarás casi todo lo necesario para tu
							cursada.
						</p>

						<div
							class="rounded-r-lg border-l-4 border-unahur-primary bg-blue-50 p-4 dark:bg-blue-900/20">
							<p class="mb-3">
								Arrancamos el cuatrimestre con una modalidad de cursada mixta,
								donde tendremos clases presenciales y virtuales. Hay que estar
								atento/a al
							</p>
							<a
								href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1sLaT8umV6RRoZzucOrxw3d3CNJuVTj22Dm4JK0wVNsg/edit?usp=sharing"
								target="_blank"
								class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-unahur-primary px-4 py-2 text-white transition-colors duration-300 hover:bg-unahur-secondary">
								📅 Cronograma de la cursada
								<svg
									class="h-4 w-4"
									fill="none"
									stroke="currentColor"
									viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path
										stroke-linecap="round"
										stroke-linejoin="round"
										stroke-width="2"
										d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"
									></path>
								</svg>
							</a>
						</div>

						<p>
							Si ya viniste varias veces, probablemente quieras ver el
							<a
								href="/material"
								class="font-semibold text-unahur-primary hover:underline dark:text-unahur-accent"
								>material</a
							>
							que tenemos disponible.
						</p>

						<div
							class="rounded-r-lg border-l-4 border-amber-400 bg-amber-50 p-4 dark:bg-amber-900/20">
							<p class="mb-3">
								<strong>⚠️ Importante:</strong> También vas a tener que instalarte:
							</p>
							<ul class="ml-4 list-inside list-disc space-y-1">
								<li>Git</li>
								<li>JDK (Java Development Kit)</li>
								<li>Maven</li>
							</ul>
							<p class="mt-3">
								En la sección <a
									href="/videos"
									class="font-semibold text-unahur-primary hover:underline dark:text-unahur-accent"
									>Videos</a
								>
								encontrarás los tutoriales para hacerlo.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="bg-white py-16 dark:bg-gray-800">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
				<div
					class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-blue-50 p-8 shadow-xl dark:border-gray-700 dark:from-gray-800 dark:to-blue-900/20">
					<div class="mb-8 text-center">
						<h2
							class="mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-unahur-primary to-unahur-secondary bg-clip-text text-3xl font-bold text-transparent">
							Canales de Comunicación
						</h2>
						<div
							class="mx-auto h-1 w-24 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-unahur-primary to-unahur-secondary">
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
						<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
							Vamos a utilizar esta página para subir material, fechas
							importantes y todo lo relacionado a la cursada. Tal vez sea una
							buena idea agregarla a los favoritos de tu navegador.
						</p>

						<div
							class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-md dark:border-gray-600 dark:bg-gray-700">
							<h3
								class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-semibold text-unahur-primary dark:text-unahur-accent">
								<svg
									class="h-6 w-6"
									fill="currentColor"
									viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path
										d="M20.317 4.3698a19.7913 19.7913 0 00-4.8851-1.5152.0741.0741 0 00-.0785.0371c-.211.3753-.4447.8648-.6083 1.2495-1.8447-.2762-3.68-.2762-5.4868 0-.1636-.3933-.4058-.8742-.6177-1.2495a.077.077 0 00-.0785-.037 19.7363 19.7363 0 00-4.8852 1.515.0699.0699 0 00-.0321.0277C.5334 9.0458-.319 13.5799.0992 18.0578a.0824.0824 0 00.0312.0561c2.0528 1.5076 4.0413 2.4228 5.9929 3.0294a.0777.0777 0 00.0842-.0276c.4616-.6304.8731-1.2952 1.226-1.9942a.076.076 0 00-.0416-.1057c-.6528-.2476-1.2743-.5495-1.8722-.8923a.077.077 0 01-.0076-.1277c.1258-.0943.2517-.1923.3718-.2914a.0743.0743 0 01.0776-.0105c3.9278 1.7933 8.18 1.7933 12.0614 0a.0739.0739 0 01.0785.0095c.1202.099.246.1981.3728.2924a.077.077 0 01-.0066.1276 12.2986 12.2986 0 01-1.873.8914.0766.0766 0 00-.0407.1067c.3604.698.7719 1.3628 1.225 1.9932a.076.076 0 00.0842.0286c1.961-.6067 3.9495-1.5219 6.0023-3.0294a.077.077 0 00.0313-.0552c.5004-5.177-.8382-9.6739-3.5485-13.6604a.061.061 0 00-.0312-.0286zM8.02 15.3312c-1.1825 0-2.1569-1.0857-2.1569-2.419 0-1.3332.9555-2.4189 2.157-2.4189 1.2108 0 2.1757 1.0952 2.1568 2.419-.019 1.3332-.9555 2.4189-2.1569 2.4189zm7.9748 0c-1.1825 0-2.1569-1.0857-2.1569-2.419 0-1.3332.9554-2.4189 2.1569-2.4189 1.2108 0 2.1757 1.0952 2.1568 2.419 0 1.3332-.9555 2.4189-2.1568 2.4189Z"
									></path>
								</svg>
								Discord - Comunicación Directa
							</h3>

							<p class="mb-4">
								Para tener una comunicación más fluida vamos a utilizar un canal
								de
								<a
									href="https://www.discordapp.com/"
									target="_blank"
									class="font-semibold text-unahur-primary hover:underline dark:text-unahur-accent"
									>Discord</a
								>.
							</p>

							<div class="space-y-4">
								<div
									class="flex items-start gap-3 rounded-lg bg-blue-50 p-3 dark:bg-blue-900/30">
									<div
										class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-unahur-primary text-sm font-bold text-white">
										1
									</div>
									<div>
										<p>
											Si aún no tenes cuenta debes registrarte ingresando
											<a
												href="https://www.discordapp.com/"
												target="_blank"
												class="font-semibold text-unahur-primary hover:underline dark:text-unahur-accent"
												>aquí</a
											>
										</p>
									</div>
								</div>

								<div
									class="flex items-start gap-3 rounded-lg bg-green-50 p-3 dark:bg-green-900/30">
									<div
										class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-unahur-primary text-sm font-bold text-white">
										2
									</div>
									<div>
										<p class="mb-2">
											Una vez registrado y dentro de Discord, debes entrar a
											este link y asegurarte de Aceptar la invitación al
											servidor de la carrera:
										</p>
										<a
											href="https://discord.gg/tqyHtPt"
											target="_blank"
											class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-unahur-primary px-4 py-2 text-sm text-white transition-colors duration-300 hover:bg-unahur-secondary">
											🏫 InformaticaUNAHUR
											<svg
												class="h-4 w-4"
												fill="none"
												stroke="currentColor"
												viewBox="0 0 24 24">
												<path
													stroke-linecap="round"
													stroke-linejoin="round"
													stroke-width="2"
													d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"
												></path>
											</svg>
										</a>
									</div>
								</div>

								<div
									class="flex items-start gap-3 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 p-3 dark:bg-purple-900/30">
									<div
										class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-unahur-primary text-sm font-bold text-white">
										3
									</div>
									<div>
										<p class="mb-2">
											Luego, siguiendo este enlace podrás matricularte en los
											canales:
										</p>
										<a
											href="https://discord.gg/XpP6kCTkFd"
											target="_blank"
											class="mb-2 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-purple-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-white transition-colors duration-300 hover:bg-purple-700">
											📝 Matricularse en materias
											<svg
												class="h-4 w-4"
												fill="none"
												stroke="currentColor"
												viewBox="0 0 24 24">
												<path
													stroke-linecap="round"
													stroke-linejoin="round"
													stroke-width="2"
													d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"
												></path>
											</svg>
										</a>
										<p class="text-sm">
											Para esta materia, corresponde <strong
												class="text-unahur-primary dark:text-unahur-accent"
												>(765) Programación de Objetos II</strong
											>. ⚠️ Asegurate de hacerlo solo 1 vez.
										</p>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div
							class="rounded-r-lg border-l-4 border-amber-400 bg-amber-50 p-4 dark:bg-amber-900/20">
							<p>
								<strong>🎓 Campus Universitario:</strong> Aunque toda la comunicación
								sobre la materia irá apareciendo en esta página, también es importante
								que revises regularmente el
								<a
									href="https://campus2025.unahur.edu.ar/login/index.php"
									target="_blank"
									class="font-semibold text-unahur-primary hover:underline dark:text-unahur-accent">
									campus de la Universidad
								</a>.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</DefaultLayout><style>
	a {
		color: var(--primary-300) !important;
	}
	p {
		margin-top: 0.7rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
	}
	h2 {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	a {
		transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out;
		cursor: pointer;
	}

	a:hover {
		transform: scale(1.1);
	}
</style>
